{"tid":2032948,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"今日好多高官9up，明日個股市實俾他們燈死","createTime":"2020-05-24T10:49:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-24T13:17:34.000Z","uid":53062,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"e84c10d3bea25d77afc8b5e7f43dbb800a3c4d3c","tid":2032948,"uid":53062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:49:55.000Z","msg":"波叔<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.fso.gov.hk/chi/blog/blog20200524.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fso.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fblog%2Fblog20200524.htm&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=fd8bb70e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.fso.gov.hk/chi/blog/blog20200524.htm</a><br />\n國家安全法的補足，是透過法律在制度上保護香港免受相關威脅，防範分裂國家或顛覆國家政權以及組織恐怖活動等的危險行為，以及阻止外國和境外勢力的干預，避免香港被利用為分裂國家的據點，避免社會走向極端化和不必要的動亂狀態，有利於保持社會安全穩定，最終將有助維持有利的營商和投資環境。<br />\n<br />\n大波驊<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/public/blog/20200524_blog1.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.doj.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Fpublic%2Fblog%2F20200524_blog1.html&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=b9c4112d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.doj.gov.hk/chi/public/blog/20200524_blog1.html</a><br />\n香港經歷了社會動盪，暴力不時發生，更甚者有人竟然鼓吹獨立。面臨國家安全局勢更加日趨嚴峻，但特區行政立法機關難以在一段可見時間內自行完成維護國家安全有關的立法，有見及此，全國人民代表大會（全國人大）從國家層面進行改善香港特別行政區維護國家安全的法律制度和執行機制。特區政府已清楚表明支持全國人大的決定，我希望藉此解釋相關法律文書當中所涉及《憲法》和《基本法》的依據。<br />\n<br />\n李家超<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/articles/articles_2020_05_24.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sb.gov.hk%2Fchi%2Farticles%2Farticles_2020_05_24.htm&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=1b6ba673\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sb.gov.hk/chi/articles/articles_2020_05_24.htm</a><br />\n但我們不能掉以輕心，政府正密切審視情況，不排除會提升恐襲威脅的級別。一旦恐襲發生或恐襲威脅級別提升，警方很可能要封鎖高風險地點、作高姿態巡邏、搜查隨身物品和在公眾地方作安全檢查，以確保公共安全，巿民須配合行動，以保障他們自身及社會安全。<br />\n<br />\n馬逢國<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3%E5%86%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E5%BE%8C%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E9%87%8B%E7%96%91-NwpGxM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Fhk%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E9%259F%2593%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%2586%2580%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25BE%258C%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259C%259F%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E8%25AE%2580%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%2589%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%2587%258B%25E7%2596%2591-NwpGxM&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=63aedbb7\" target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/hk/pc/article/%E9%9F%93%E6%AD%A3%E5%86%80%E4%BA%BA%E5%A4%A7%E5%9B%9E%E6%B8%AF%E5%BE%8C%E8%AA%8D%E7%9C%9F%E8%A7%A3%E8%AE%80%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E9%87%8B%E7%96%91-NwpGxM</a><br />\n主要是針對違法搞港獨、分裂、暴力衝擊和引進外國勢力的行為，只涉及極少數人，目的是要保護大多數港人的正常生活及權益不受侵害。<br />\n<br />\n「香港各界撐國安立法聯合陣線」<br />\n<a href=\"https://info.signforhk2020.com/post/23\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finfo.signforhk2020.com%2Fpost%2F23&d=e%2FZn%2FRm8DA7JC3c9yYGDtQhG%2BHbubzuYLsHMVHmGZzU%3D&h=fef23744\" target=\"_blank\">https://info.signforhk2020.com/post/23</a><br />\n有商界人士透露，有業界人士在經歷過去一年的黑暴事件後，已做好移民的準備，但上週知悉本港將有國安法的消息，立即燃起了他對香港的希望，取消所有移民安排，用實際行動投下對香港未來的信心一票。<br />\n<br />\n死得，他們愈講愈令人不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4dcc2b0a182acc0635b0664cf4dd5128b3d98d8","tid":2032948,"uid":53156,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"究竟佢地定連登仔燈力強d<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc61999926131b893fd0979b88de7818f39c980a","tid":2032948,"uid":62512,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T10:51:30.000Z","msg":"佢地講到香港而家好危險, 有恐怖襲擊, 同敍利亞一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff5aab164f0a80a01ce54901b5772e852eaf40ce","tid":2032948,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi